For the latest news, visit the SparForte web site.

Objective: Foundation for value meta labels (Phase 2)

Known Issues

SparForte will run slower because of the value meta labels checking at run-time.

CHANGES SINCE 3.0

1. Fix: In files.is_execute/is_execute file, the group execute permission is now checked.

2. Fix: In files.is_readable and other functions that check readability, in edge cases where the kernel getlogin() fails and, in turn, group_member() fails, the read access checks fall back to checking the simple file gid againt the user's effective gid.  Comments also fixed in c_os.c.


